											<pre _ngcontent-anj-c150="" class="text ris-text ris-copy-src main_content_citetext">TY  - JOUR
T1  - Evolving Adversarial Training (EAT) for AI-Powered Intrusion Detection Systems (IDS)

AU  - Ahmed Muktadir Affan
Y1  - 2024/09/29
